ler)|Nelson]] {{goal|74}}|team2=[[Ayr United F.C.|Ayr United]]|goals2=|stadium=[[Dens Park]], [[Dundee]]|location=|attendance=5,520|referee=Alan Newlands|result=W}}{{Football box collapsible|id=|date=24 August 2019|time=15:00|round=3|score=0\u20130|report=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49379023|team1=Dundee|goals1=|team2=[[Inverness Caledonian Thistle F.C.|Inverness Caledonian Thistle]]|goals2=|stadium=[[Dens Park]], [[Dundee]]|location=|attendance=5,016|referee=David Munro|result=D}}{{Football box collapsible|id=|date=30 August 2019|time=19:45|round=4|score=[[Dundee derby|6\u20132]]|report=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/49443612|team1=[[Dundee United F.C.|Dundee United]]|goals1=[[Calum Butcher|Butcher]] {{goal|14||40}} <br> [[Louis App\u00e9r\u00e9|App\u00e9r\u00e9]] {{goal|33}} <br> [[Lawrence Shankland|Shankland]] {{goal|36|pen.}} <br> [[Ian Harkes|Harkes]] {{goal|46}} <br> [[Cammy Smith|C. Smith]] {{goal|83}}|team2=Dundee|goals2=[[Kane Hemmings|Hemmings]] {{goal|22}} <br> [[Andrew Nelson (footballer)|Nelson]] {{goal|70}}|stadium=[[Tannadice Park]], [[Dundee]]|location=|attendance=14,108|referee=[[Kevin Clancy]]|result=L}}{{Football box collapsible|id=|date=14 September 2019|time=15:00|round=5|score=2\u20131|report=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49618118|team1=Dundee|goals1=[[Danny Johnson (footballer)|Johnson]] {{goal|2}} <br> [[Jordan McGhee|McGhee]] {{goal|39}}|team2=[[Alloa Athletic F.C.|Alloa Athletic]]|goals2=[[Liam Dick|Dick]] {{goal|10}}|stadium=[[Dens Park]], [[Dundee]]|location=|attendance=4,453|referee=Alan Newlands|result=W}}{{Football box collapsible|id=|date=21 September 2019|time=15:00|round=6|score=1\u20130|report=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49698676|team1=[[Greenock Morton F.C.|Greenock Morton]]|goals1=[[Peter Grant (footballer, born 1994)|Grant]] {{goal|45+1}}|team2=Dundee|goals2=|stadium=[[Cappielow]], [[Greenock]]|location=|attendance=1,901|referee=[[John McKendrick]]|result=L}}{{Football box collapsible|id=|date=27 Se