reichischen Bundesministerium f\u00fcr Heereswesen und vom Kriegsarchiv |trans-title=Austria-Hungary's Last War, 1914\u20131918 |volume=VII |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |year=1938 |publisher=\u00d6sterreichischen Bundesministerium f\u00fcr Herrswesen [Published by the Austrian Federal Ministry of Military Affairs and the War Archive] |location=Vienna |edition=online |others=trans. Stan Hanna |url=http://www.comroestudios.com/StanHanna/Vol7.pdf |accessdate=3 May 2015 |oclc=557493618}}\n* {{cite book |last=Shellum |first=Brian G. |title=African American Officers in Liberia: A Pestiferous Rotation, 1910-1942|authorlink= |year=2018 |publisher=University of Nebraska Press}}\n* {{cite book |title=Statistics of the Military Effort of the British Empire During the Great War 1914\u20131920 |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |year=1922 |publisher=[[HMSO]] |location=London |edition= |url=https://archive.org/details/statisticsofmili00grea |accessdate=4 March 2017 |oclc=924169428}}\n* {{cite book |title=World War I: A History |last=Strachan |first=Hew |authorlink=Hew Strachan |year=1999 |publisher=Oxford University Press |location=London |isbn=978-0-19-820614-9 |url=https://archive.org/details/worldwarihistory00stra }}\n* {{cite book |last=Traxel |first=David |title=Crusader Nation: The United States in Peace and the Great War |authorlink= |year=2006 |publisher=Random House, Inc. |location=New York |isbn=9780375724657}}\n* {{cite book |last=Tucker |first=Spencer C. |title=The European Powers in the First World War: An Encyclopaedia |authorlink= |year=1999 |publisher=Garland |location=New York |isbn=978-0-8153-3351-7}}\n* {{cite book |last=Tucker |first=Spencer C. |title=World War I: A Student Encyclopedia |authorlink= |year=2006 |publisher=ABC-CLIO |location=New York |isbn=9781851098798}}\n* {{cite book |last=Urlanis |first=Boris |title=Wars and Population |authorlink= |year=1971 |publisher=Progress |location=Moscow |oclc=579400}}\n* Ward, Steven R. (2014