erly, Carol R.: [https://encyclopedia.1914-1918-online.net/article/war_losses_usa War Losses (USA)], in: [https://encyclopedia.1914-1918-online.net/home/ 1914-1918-online. International Encyclopedia of the First World War].\n* Cook, Tim, Stewart, William: [https://encyclopedia.1914-1918-online.net/article/war_losses_canada War Losses (Canada)], in: [https://encyclopedia.1914-1918-online.net/home/ 1914-1918-online. International Encyclopedia of the First World War].\n* Ba\u015f, Mehmet Fatih: [https://encyclopedia.1914-1918-online.net/article/war_losses_ottoman_empiremiddle_east War Losses (Ottoman Empire/Middle East)], in: [https://encyclopedia.1914-1918-online.net/home/ 1914-1918-online. International Encyclopedia of the First World War].\n* Tepora, Tuomas.: [https://encyclopedia.1914-1918-online.net/article/finnish_civil_war_1918 Finnish Civil War], in: [https://encyclopedia.1914-1918-online.net/home/ 1914-1918-online. International Encyclopedia of the First World War].\n* Ponce, Javier: [https://encyclopedia.1914-1918-online.net/article/spain Spain] , in: [https://encyclopedia.1914-1918-online.net/home/ 1914-1918-online. International Encyclopedia of the First World War]\n* [http://necrometrics.com/20c5m.htm#WW1 World War I casualties from Historical Atlas of the Twentieth Century]\n* [http://longwaytotipperary.ul.ie/ Long way to Tipperary- an Irish story of the great war]\n* [https://uboat.net/ A database of Allied and neutral ships sunk by German U-boats in both world wars]\n* [https://smallwarsjournal.com/jrnl/art/caribbean-theater-haiti-and-first-world-war Haitian involvement in World War I]\n\n{{World War I}}\n\n[[Category:World War I casualties| ]]\n[[Category:Aftermath of World War I]]\n[[Category:Demographic history]]\n", "name_user": "76.76.66.128", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_War_I_casualties"}
